{"tid":2031094,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"獨媒收律師信，涉違反高等法院禁制令","createTime":"2020-05-23T07:26:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T09:51:53.000Z","uid":27797,"like":28,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9e488e14933e0246a58bb975636d94cb64a5219d","tid":2031094,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T07:26:41.000Z","msg":"因為岑敖暉一篇文搞到又要拉人又要封艇，國安法未到都搞鳩左你先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1073722?fbclid=IwAR0joJIIG6dAE28xSl1lESisnDRPZ6D3NqjzwZ3kHozVeoEjGgbdzbGqvE4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1073722%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0joJIIG6dAE28xSl1lESisnDRPZ6D3NqjzwZ3kHozVeoEjGgbdzbGqvE4&d=s%2ByQnOBpfLb1r8GSWDTSOV3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=cf5f386d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1073722%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0joJIIG6dAE28xSl1lESisnDRPZ6D3NqjzwZ3kHozVeoEjGgbdzbGqvE4&h=2ec374d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1073722?fbclid=IwAR0joJIIG6dAE28xSl1lESisnDRPZ6D3NqjzwZ3kHozVeoEjGgbdzbGqvE4</a><br />\n<br />\n香港獨立媒體網<br />\n<br />\n網站聲明<br />\n<br />\n本網今日收到律政司來信，指5月9日荃灣區議員岑敖暉在本網的一篇文章，違反高等法院禁制令，要求在七日內回覆。<br />\n<br />\n本網會暫時將該文章下架，並盡快索取法律意見，商討下一步行動。<br />\n<br />\n香港人這幾日過得不容易，大家保重。<br />\n<br />\n2020年5月23日"},{"pid":"11133adfc5974be69e7dc5d18a06a81596a738e2","tid":2031094,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T07:27:05.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"0d22f7dfdff4c10793c16e519191682e7a3b911f","tid":2031094,"uid":2054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T07:27:12.000Z","msg":"黑警殺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"218478885b33289c890f7d6d2284e38d0a9c695c","tid":2031094,"uid":27797,"like":1,"dislike":0,"sco